snippet: Spain plans to hand over a close ally of the former Egyptian president Hosni Mubarak to Egyptian authorities to face corruption charges, Egyptian state television reported Monday.

lead_paragraph: Spain plans to hand over a close ally of the former Egyptian president Hosni Mubarak to Egyptian authorities to face corruption charges, Egyptian state television reported Monday.

headline.main: Egypt: Spain Will Return Mubarak Ally to Face Corruption Charges, Report Says
headline.print_headline: Egypt: Spain Will Return Mubarak Ally To Face Corruption Charges, Report Says
